{"tid":354841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]淘寶啲客服真係好撚搞笑","createTime":"2017-08-10T19:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T21:00:17.000Z","uid":45790,"like":34,"dislike":241,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"129532cbec20baeb7904dea627b64488e0926722","tid":354841,"uid":45790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:37:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的 早排係淘寶呢間鋪買左兩件衫<br />\n兩件個款都ok 但兩件都分別有啲問題<br />\n於是我就比左個中評佢<br />\n過左日個客服就開始同我講野 要我del左個評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我梗係睬佢都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直頭唔覆佢<br />\n點知佢由6月25 講到7月24 足足一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個内容真係笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/033401_c05fdc9899a607c9896d77a4a8ebd183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F033401_c05fdc9899a607c9896d77a4a8ebd183.jpg&h=27af1e49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/033402_ce76bf12ab7f6535f6e8583ab1c63c41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F033402_ce76bf12ab7f6535f6e8583ab1c63c41.jpg&h=8cb6bd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/033403_c51bf7596b95a75e8f3d6116ead19a5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F033403_c51bf7596b95a75e8f3d6116ead19a5c.jpg&h=7d364358&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/033404_f7496b47cc6bfeaa779667b5d0469acf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F033404_f7496b47cc6bfeaa779667b5d0469acf.jpg&h=36447ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/033404_ca7ed21ea5133240b21cf9d9831aa069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F033404_ca7ed21ea5133240b21cf9d9831aa069.jpg&h=fe09dcbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/033420_714aae3792003e252efcf627e8f73deb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F033420_714aae3792003e252efcf627e8f73deb.jpg&h=e6f76f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢之後就冇再同我講野 唔知佢係咪已經執包袱走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa52bc0e79d2d51c9c7cd594cb1956c377152e7b","tid":354841,"uid":132225,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:41:08.000Z","msg":"有潛則做地產"},{"pid":"2090b53c977c0b0b6770d05d8f27913365ca1a3e","tid":354841,"uid":129039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:45:33.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"0bc86bd867a8aea86ab217c8fc7e4a2c34b67ca2","tid":354841,"uid":65587,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:50:57.000Z","msg":"評論不能解決問題<br />\n但能解決你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351cb0c0c707851e9765de992630786b998e26d9","tid":354841,"uid":34714,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:52:10.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec6ad9aa74fad9343975b664e2748ad5531ff91","tid":354841,"uid":73077,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:53:38.000Z","msg":"聽聞係啲客服每日有個target要收到幾多好評先可以收工/有獎金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c400f76d2d29b0bdf391cc5868af5004eff5aaec","tid":354841,"uid":126506,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:55:36.000Z","msg":"好似幾慘 雖然佢都係copy and paste"},{"pid":"0493460b96d5d79adf482b7175f01b5ce1acf23c","tid":354841,"uid":45790,"like":90,"dislike":4,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽聞係啲客服每日有個target要收到幾多好評先可以收工/有獎金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢件貨冇問題自然會比好評啦 但有問題既唔通我仲要因爲個客服話自己好慘就作番個好評比佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我已經唔係比差評係比中評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1452b61c8b520d28c4ace594692fce47a4c3c68c","tid":354841,"uid":81791,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/040533_689d6cfb206ff4dcc87d06d5058343cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F040533_689d6cfb206ff4dcc87d06d5058343cb.jpg&h=ac405955&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/040534_42c0b31ba912f26e0ba591507f55aaf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F040534_42c0b31ba912f26e0ba591507f55aaf2.jpg&h=ca33a304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾得個2、3蚊 不如唔撚好俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c97830a230d99988497dfa17f80cf23844ad1c","tid":354841,"uid":132638,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/040947_182032f0aca772a9d0f8929c422dbcd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F040947_182032f0aca772a9d0f8929c422dbcd7.jpg&h=1f066ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買咗百幾蚊野，無俾兩個配件,成舊嘢唔用得又唔補返俾我都夠膽叫我del差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7d030eb45a33ff21d2e1c98edcb01f6ce43746","tid":354841,"uid":74380,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:16:54.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為左個評價成個乞兒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係有咁重要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申未用過淘寶"},{"pid":"0109e2607fb03ebe9b027954aa0ec977b551fc20","tid":354841,"uid":45790,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/040533_689d6cfb206ff4dcc87d06d5058343cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F040533_689d6cfb206ff4dcc87d06d5058343cb.jpg&h=ac405955&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/040534_42c0b31ba912f26e0ba591507f55aaf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F040534_42c0b31ba912f26e0ba591507f55aaf2.jpg&h=ca33a304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾得個2、3蚊 不如唔撚好俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我買件衫番嚟條吊帶短到著唔到 free size唔係我買錯size<br />\n我唔想浪費仲要自己加工加長條帶先著到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0653b8570e83c99839eaadd8845c04fb9c1f437b","tid":354841,"uid":45790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/040947_182032f0aca772a9d0f8929c422dbcd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F040947_182032f0aca772a9d0f8929c422dbcd7.jpg&h=1f066ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買咗百幾蚊野，無俾兩個配件,成舊嘢唔用得又唔補返俾我都夠膽叫我del差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都已經唔係比差評佢 只係中評 都想我del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2731c4f494f20cc839ce6f78b8d92c60a6055e58","tid":354841,"uid":50767,"like":18,"dislike":100,"score":-82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:34:07.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得你好撚賤 人地打工你就撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"f56b085da54c1e9ad43855a7bfe6345e98cef13f","tid":354841,"uid":3302,"like":6,"dislike":31,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係覺得你好撚賤 人地打工你就撚狗咁撚</blockquote><br />\n證明港女都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140bd94efc9f1e37b342651a194b7ebe695af648","tid":354841,"uid":17370,"like":23,"dislike":9,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係覺得你好撚賤 人地打工你就撚狗咁撚</blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n樓主理都冇理過佢喎 點樣撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何況支那人沒有一個是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3edbbdabe7f97b49e2cedf81900703fab136146","tid":354841,"uid":96743,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係覺得你好撚賤 人地打工你就撚狗咁撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨不對版比差評有錯？<br />\n樓主有回覆過佢？<br />\n殺手殺人都係打份工  係咪因為咁就唔洗坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b8630ae0091b9652acca46eb95afcbccb17e45","tid":354841,"uid":56594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T20:50:01.000Z","msg":"求求您了小仙女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022b08f76ad118f33b2707d000f34f0c4d456e4e","tid":354841,"uid":79502,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T21:00:56.000Z","msg":"乜講到咁慘呀，我又未試過喎，我呢邊傾到要結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/t09r7sli\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft09r7sli&h=449787ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uw6r791k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuw6r791k&h=e28f619e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rskbxcjv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frskbxcjv&h=cf1f1cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zip9rwtd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzip9rwtd&h=7a7e7698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2229d9581598c85caa6a8149535c0f889997f616","tid":354841,"uid":84507,"like":19,"dislike":8,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T21:05:31.000Z","msg":"淘寶有邊間唔係全部五星先有人買.......<br />\n同你去搵酒店一樣，<a href=\"http://唔通Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%94%94%E9%80%9AHotels.com&d=QjXhIALYWH3nY7IovSA5Xv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=79a268c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">唔通Hotels.com</a> 四星果D 你敢住？除左冇錢窮咁就無計<br />\n唔係五星評價果D 酒店其實已經唔住得人咁滯<br />\n<br />\n唔好話淘寶Amazon 都係，舊野少過四星半你唔係夠膽買下話？中伏唔好喊喎！<br />\n<br />\n唔比五星佢咁樣做又真係於心何忍既<br />\n不過唔係有我地咁做，大家邊會知佢地真係有做錯？<br />\n夾硬比五星佢唔單止自己條氣唔順，仲累埋全部買野既人一齊仆街中伏<br />\n唔想做不孝子就自己醒醒定定講心果句<br />\n我撐你架！<br />\n<br />\n同埋上面果D 已經算好<br />\n上次毒果直頭當新聞大陸條客服日日打來屌鳩條友點解唔比五星"},{"pid":"8cba144e2435cf23e68c1edcb54ac12f3cb4db36","tid":354841,"uid":79502,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T21:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 早排係淘寶呢間鋪買左兩件衫<br />\n兩件個款都ok 但兩件都分別有啲問題<br />\n於是我就比左個中評佢<br />\n過左日個客服就開始同我講野 要我del左個評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我梗係睬佢都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直頭唔覆佢<br />\n點知佢由6月25 講到7月24 足足一個月<img src=\"/assets/face